sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant KC as Keycloak
    participant V as Viewer Count Service
    participant K as Kafka
    participant R as Redis

    Note over U,R: 0. Authentication

U->>KC: POST /login {username, password}
KC-->>U: accessToken + refreshToken
Note over U: extracts userId from accessToken

    Note over U,R: 1. Join Stream

    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/join {userId}
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>K: publish ViewerJoined {streamId, userId, timestamp}
        V-->>U: 200 OK
        K->>V: consume ViewerJoined
        V->>R: SADD stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
        R-->>V: 1 (new) or 0 (duplicate)
        alt new viewer
            V->>R: INCR viewer_count
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        else duplicate
            V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
        end
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over U,R: 2. Heartbeat

    loop every 30s
        U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/heartbeat {userId}
        V->>V: validate JWT token
        V->>K: publish ViewerHeartbeat {streamId, userId}
        K->>V: consume ViewerHeartbeat
        V->>R: SETEX viewer:{userId} 60
    end

    Note over U,R: 3. Leave Stream

    U->>V: POST /streams/{streamId}/leave {userId}
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>K: publish ViewerLeft {streamId, userId, timestamp}
        V-->>U: 200 OK
        K->>V: consume ViewerLeft
        V->>R: SREM stream:{streamId}:viewers {userId}
        R-->>V: 1 (removed) or 0 (not found)
        alt removed
            V->>R: DECR viewer_count
            V->>R: DEL viewer:{userId}
        else not found
            Note over V: Ignore
        end
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over V,R: 4. Ghost User

    R->>V: EXPIRED viewer:{userId}
    V->>R: SISMEMBER viewers {userId}
    R-->>V: 1 or 0
    alt exists
        V->>R: SREM viewers {userId}
        V->>R: DECR viewer_count
    else already removed
        Note over V: Ignore
    end

    Note over U,R: 5. Get Viewer Count

    U->>V: GET /streams/{streamId}/viewers
    V->>V: validate JWT token
    alt token valid
        V->>R: GET viewer_count
        R-->>V: N
        V-->>U: 200 OK {viewerCount: N}
    else token invalid
        V-->>U: 401 Unauthorized
    end